and-grow-as-a-celo-content-creator">Create, earn, and grow as a Celo content creator<a class="hash-link" href="#create-earn-and-grow-as-a-celo-content-creator" title="Direct link to heading">â€‹</a></h2><p>Celo Sages are Celo community members who are passionate about expanding Celoâ€™s mission of prosperity for all. They are developers, educators and content creators interested in creating and sharing technical content with the Celo community.</p><p>âœ… <a href="/community/celo-sage/submit-application">Submit an application</a></p><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip alert alert--success admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>tip</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><p>Need to request technical content from a Celo Sage? Fill out the <a href="https://forms.gle/Y53FGt4qyJ461yJ87" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">content request form</a>!</p></div></div><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="why-become-a-celo-sage">Why become a Celo Sage?<a class="hash-link" href="#why-become-a-celo-sage" title="Direct link to heading">â€‹</a></h2><ul><li><strong>Create:</strong> Write blogs, documentation, videos, or designs to help developers build on Celo.</li><li><strong>Earn:</strong> Receive bounties (Up to 500 cUSD) from your work, learn and earn for your contributions to the ecosystem.</li><li><strong>Grow:</strong> Work closely with members of the Celo Community to find new opportunities.</li></ul><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="what-youll-create">What you&#x27;ll create<a class="hash-link" href="#what-youll-create" title="Direct link to heading">â€‹</a></h2><ul class="contains-task-list containsTaskList_mC6p"><li class="task-list-item"><input type="checkbox" checked="" disabled=""> <strong>Documentation:</strong> Create reference materials for Celo Tools and products.</li><li class="task-list-item"><input type="checkbox" checked="" disabled=""> <strong>Blogs:</strong> Write updates and announcements for the Celo community.</li><li class="task-list-item"><input type="checkbox" checked="" disabled=""> <strong>Tutorials:</strong> Build project based tutorials to support Celo Developers.</li><li class="task-list-item"><input type="checkbox" checked="" disabled=""> <strong>Videos:</strong> Produce step-by-step video tutorials to improve the Celo Developer experience.</li><li class="task-list-item"><input type="checkbox" checked="" disabled=""> <strong>Presentations:</strong> Prepare presentations for events or live demonstrations.</li></ul><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip alert alert--success admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>tip</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><p>View the <a href="/tutorials">Celo Development Tutorials</a> for examples of our work.</p></div></div><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="how-it-works">How it works<a class="hash-link" href="#how-it-works" title="Direct link to heading">â€‹</a></h2><ul><li><strong>Submit application</strong>: Complete the <a href="https://forms.gle/nhQfkXZygrb3YFRs9" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">application form</a> to be considered for the program.</li><li><strong>Create content</strong>: Suggest new ideas or pick up requests from our <a href="https://trello.com/invite/b/IVRaj2QO/ATTI2d1247ea85d4c68a97451aefbcdd0e4f61AE76DC/celo-sage" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">public roadmap</a>.</li><li><strong>Earn rewards</strong>: Earn between 200-500 cUSD by submitting approved content to our <a href="https://github.com/celo-org/docs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.</li></ul><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip alert alert--success admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>tip</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><p>Reward amounts are determined before work begins and cannot be changed after getting started on the project. No more than 500 cUSD will be awarded for a project. Please keep this in mind when defining the scope of your work.</p></div></div><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="payments">Payments<a class="hash-link" href="#payments" title="Direct link to heading">â€‹</a></h2><p>Payments are awarded in cUSD to your Wallet Address based on the projects you complete. These may either be paid per project or per length of engagement as defined in your project scope.</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="additional-resources">Additional Resources<a class="hash-link" href="#additional-resources" title="Direct link to heading">â€‹</a></h2><p>Explore these resources to learn more about the Celo Sage program.</p><ul><li><a href="/blog/tutorials/introducing-celo-sage">Introducing Celo Sage</a></li><li><a href="https://trello.com/invite/b/IVRaj2QO/ATTI2d1247ea85d4c68a97451aefbcdd0e4f61AE76DC/celo-sage" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Roadmap</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/celo-org/docs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li></ul><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip alert alert--success admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>tip</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><p>Contact us on <a href="https://discord.com/invite/6yWMkgM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Discord</a> at <strong>#celo-sage</strong> for more information.</p></div></div></div><footer class="theme-doc-footer docusaurus-mt-lg"><div class="theme-doc-footer-edit-meta-row row"><div class="col"><a href="https://github.com/celo-org/docs/edit/main/docs/community/celo-sage/celo-sage.md" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="theme-edit-this-page"><svg fill="currentColor" height="20" width="20" viewBox="0 0 40 40" class="iconEdit_Z9Sw" aria-hidden="true"><g>